<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.7">
<l>niṉṟa varaiyuṅ kiṭanta kaṭalun ticaiyu mirunilaṉum</l>
<l>oṉṟu moḻiyā vaṇṇa meṇṇi niṉṟa vammāṉār</l>
<l>kuṉṟu kuṭaiyā veṭutta vaṭika ḷuṭaiya tirunāmam</l>
<l>naṉṟu kāṇmiṉ toṇṭīr coṉṉēṉ namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, perceive well the divine names of the lord who endured</l>
<l>Conceiving in a way that did not leave out anything, the stalwart mountains,</l>
<l>Sprawling seas, the quarters, and the vast land,</l>
<l>The deity who took up a hill as an umbrella; I said the Namo Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
